Check for Power
Difficulty: BasicAccuracy: 34.59%Submissions: 65K+Points: 1
Given two positive integers x and y, determine if y is a power of x. If y is a power of x, return true. Otherwise, return false.










class Solution {
  public:
    bool isPower(int x, int y) {
        
      float a = float(log2(y)/log2(x));
      return pow(x,a)==y;
      }
};
